34 likes, 20 comments - amanda_coffee_books on July 9, 2024: "Good Morning Coffee Friends, Christmas in July 
Peppermint Mexican Chocolate Hot Coffee
Thank you to @back_house_syrup for sending me these amazing syrups. 
I am using the last of Colombian Blend. Really been loving this beans. 
I do have a link & Promo codes for the coffee beans.⤵️
https://www.sunrisecoffeecollective.com

1/2 tbsp Peppermint 
1/2 scoop Mexican Spiced Chocolate 
6oz Colombian Blend (Sunrise Coffee Collective) 
1/2 Hot Milk ( lactose free) 
Homemade Peppermint Whipped Cream 
Cocoa Powder 
Chocolate curls 
Crushed Peppermint 
.
